			a(href="http://www.bidnetwork.org") Visit their site 

		li.pure-u-1-3: .partner
			a.logo(href="http://unreasonableinstitute.org/", target="_blank")
				img(alt="Unreasonable institute"
					src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/moving_worlds/partner+logos/Unreasonable_logo.png")
